Key Match Events: Rinku Singh and Prasidh Krishna made their T20I debuts for India against Ireland on August 18, 2023.
Jasprit Bumrah returned to the team after an 11-month injury layoff.
Prasidh Krishna, who has 25 wickets in 14 ODIs, made his T20I debut.
Rinku Singh played his first ever international match.
Bumrah won the toss and elected to bowl against Ireland.
Ireland included pacer Craig Young in their playing XI.
